These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Hobby: sudoku, filmmaking
Job: musician, freelancer
1. Job:musician is in an even position##4
2. Job:freelancer == Hobby:filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | sudoku |
| Job     | freelancer    | musician   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Beverage: almond-milk, milk
Sport: skateboarding, snowboarding
1. Sport:skateboarding is in an odd position##4
2. Beverage:milk is on the left of Beverage:almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | milk | almond-milk        |
| Sport      | skateboarding  | snowboarding |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
Music-Genre: blues, metal
Nationality: indian, colombian
